          "order": 1,
          "title": "",
          "summary": "The scrutiny on Worldcoin continues. The Argentine Agency for Access to Public Information (AAIP) has initiated an investigation to ascertain the legality of its data collection practices. It wants entities like Worldcoin to register with the organization, provide information about its data processing policies, and indicate the purpose for collecting sensitive data and the retention period for such data. The AAIP did not confirm whether Worldcoin complies with the standards.",
